(
  'King Fahd Library: Everything You Need to Know',
  'king-fahd-library-everything-you-need-to-know',
  'Complete guide to King Fahd National Library in Riyadh — the building, collections, opening hours, and how to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521587760476-6c12a4b040da?w=900&q=80" alt="King Fahd National Library Riyadh interior" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>King Fahd Library: Everything You Need to Know</h2>
<p>King Fahd National Library is one of Riyadh''s most recognisable modern buildings, wrapped in a distinctive tent-like glass and steel facade on King Fahd Road. Beyond its architecture, it serves as Saudi Arabia''s main legal deposit library, holding an extensive collection of Arabic and international works, manuscripts, and periodicals.</p>
