<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Book sunset time slots at least a day ahead — they sell out fastest</li><li>The floor has a partial glass section for photos, but skip it if you''re not comfortable with heights</li><li>Tickets can typically be bought online in advance or at the counter on Level 4</li><li>Pair your visit with dinner at one of the mall''s upper-floor restaurants afterward</li></ul>
