<h2>Riyadh Winter Wonderland: A Complete Guide</h2>
<p>Riyadh Winter Wonderland is a seasonal snow-and-ice attraction that appears each year as part of the Riyadh Season programme, bringing ice skating rinks, snow play areas, and festive lighting to the capital during the cooler months. It''s a popular family outing precisely because it offers an experience rarely available elsewhere in the Gulf.</p>
